metadata.name: Luzia
metadata.description: Luzia is a Baroque-style artwork that embodies the burden of modernity. Using a blend of artificial intelligence and digital painting, evoking a palpable atmosphere of despair. The dramatic lighting, typical of Bellini's style, enhances the feeling of discomfort and melancholy. Luzia seems to be lost in thought, struggling internally. This artwork illustrates how the modern world is complex and generates tensions in our lives.
